To address the climate crisis, we need to deal with our addiction to oil, coal &amp; gas.

In the 21st century we are paying for our crippling reliance on 19th century technology. 

@UNDP explains why we need to break up with fossil fuels: https://t.co/4yvScDflk9 #ClimateAction https://t.co/dP8xoP1oml

Lead exposure affects human health, especially in children. 

Even low-level exposure can cause lifelong health problems to the central nervous system, brain and other vital organs.

@WHO has more during International Lead Poisoning Prevention Week. https://t.co/3L26GYbtH1 https://t.co/lZT5gC2zbS

